des: Planning and having a baby is a serious decision that must be taken with great responsibility. The whole pregnancy is a very exciting process. Our daily tips will decorate your everyday life and help you find the answers to many questions. The information in this skill is provided for informational and educational purposes only. This tool does not provide medical advice, and is for informational and educational purposes only, and is not a substitute for professional medical advice, treatment or diagnosis. Call your doctor to receive medical advice. If you think you may have a medical emergency, please dial your local emergency response phone number.
